OL,3,CAnti-sewage campaigners turn-out for
OL,4,Cpaddle out protests
OL,6,FThe charity said hundreds of water
OL,7,Fusers across the South West took part,
OL,8,Fcalling for an end to raw sewage
OL,9,Fdischarge in waterways and clearer
OL,10,Fmonitoring and transparency of sewage
OL,11,Fspills.
OL,13,FSouth West Water said it has been
OL,14,Ffocused on reducing spills at beaches
OL,15,Fin the bathing season by 20% in the
OL,16,Flast five years.
OL,18,FRaw sewage spilled into England's
OL,19,Frivers and seas for a record 3.6
OL,20,Fmillion hours in 2024, according to
OL,21,Ffigures from the Environment Agency.
