OL,3,CAnti-sewage campaigners turn-out for
OL,4,Cpaddle out protests
OL,6,FGiles Bristow, CEO at Surfers Against
OL,7,FSewage, said: "Another year, another
OL,8,Fsummer of swimming and surfing in
OL,9,Fsewage while our shameless water
OL,10,Fcompanies laugh all the way to the
OL,11,Fbank."
OL,13,FHe added: "Our failing water industry
OL,14,Fhas been trumpeting billions in
OL,15,Finvestment to clean up their act, but
OL,16,Fwe know that these fat cat bosses
OL,17,Fcan't be trusted to keep their
OL,18,Fpromises."
