OL,3,CAnti-sewage campaigners turn-out for
OL,4,Cpaddle out protests
OL,6,FSouth West Water said the views of its
OL,7,Fcustomers "matter hugely" and it
OL,8,F"fully respects" the rights of those
OL,9,Fwho wish to protest.
OL,11,FA spokesperson added: "We were one of
OL,12,Fonly five companies in the industry to
OL,13,Freduce spills compared to 2023.
OL,15,F"Our focus has been to reduce spills
OL,16,Fat beaches in the bathing season by
OL,17,F20% in the last five years as we
OL,18,Fcontinue to focus on what our
OL,19,Fcustomers care about.
